imdb.title: Lotta på Liseberg
plot: Lotta at Liseberg is a live music show with singalong with the audience from the amusement park Liseberg in Gothenburg. During the first two seasons they also played bingo in the program but the game was removed to the third season.::Anonymous
synopsis: Lotta på Liseberg is a live music show with Sing-along on the main stage at the Liseberg amusement park in Gothenburg. It is held annually since 2004 on Monday evenings in June, July and August. Since 2009 are the events shown on television.
